HEADWORD: Improvided
<hw>Im`pro*vid"ed</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Unforeseen;
unexpected; not provided against; unprepared.</def>
<mark>[Obs.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>All <qex>improvided</qex> for dread of death.</q> <rj><qau>E.
